{"tid":20502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★戰鬥民族！當年蘇聯用bubugi來逼供！","createTime":"2016-12-03T11:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T09:53:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b917b6ed14f7d540cae0774e92b93163b47e0d02","tid":20502,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:33:12.000Z","msg":"想出各種各樣的折磨方法逼迫犯人承認自己頭上的莫須有罪名。例如呵癢，就是把犯人的手腳綁起來或按住，用羽毛往鼻子裡呵癢，囚犯立馬便天旋地轉，產生一種感覺，仿佛是在往腦子裡鑽孔。再如臭蟲隔離室，在漆黑的木板釘的匣子裡，繁殖成百成千隻臭蟲，將犯人關進去並扒掉衣服，頓時間飢餓的臭蟲便爬到犯人身上，起初犯人還猛烈地同臭蟲戰鬥，過了幾小時以後就精疲力竭，乖乖地讓臭蟲吸血了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/history/3bxyla.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhistory%2F3bxyla.html&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a01dd21a\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/history/3bxyla.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4a0cb344564a448e00e8096fc296c2e9094bbd","tid":20502,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://jp.netcdn.space/digital/video/nkd00158/nkd00158jp-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjp.netcdn.space%2Fdigital%2Fvideo%2Fnkd00158%2Fnkd00158jp-3.jpg&h=dce02ec1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60dd1704b503de212e238a7ea618198baca52604","tid":20502,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:59:32.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"97348c4f500662f860df1bca873d0fa597b0877b","tid":20502,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:03:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fee537d42e6ee38da9538fd1f9073951a798a2","tid":20502,"uid":34098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":